OL,3,CMP calls for public inquiry into
OL,4,C'problems' at West Midlands Fire
OL,5,CAuthority
OL,7,FThe MP for Aldridge-Brownhills has
OL,8,Fasked for an independent public
OL,9,Finquiry into the West Midlands Fire
OL,10,FAuthority as she criticised "deep
OL,11,Frooted and troubling problems" at the
OL,12,Fservice.
OL,14,FThe West Midlands Fire Service has
OL,15,Frecently experienced tension and
OL,16,Fturmoil at the top with the
OL,17,Fresignation of its Chairman, Greg
OL,18,FBrackenridge, and interim CEO, Oliver
OL,19,FLee.
OL,26,@rD@]OUsD@^O]
