OL,7,FThe former Royal Marine commander had
OL,8,Fbeen appointed after the service's
OL,9,Fprevious chief, Wayne Brown, committed
OL,10,Fsuicide in January.
OL,12,FWendy Morton told the Commons that
OL,13,Frecent issues at the authority, which
OL,14,Foversees the running of the West
OL,15,FMidlands Fire Service, highlighted
OL,16,Fsevere shortcomings.
OL,18,F"I'm afraid there are too many
OL,19,Funanswered questions"
