OL,5,CAuthority
OL,7,F"So will this Government ensure that
OL,8,Fthere's an independent and
OL,9,Ftransparency public inquiry to ensure
OL,10,Fthat the West Midlands Fire Authority
OL,11,Fmeets the obligations and standards
OL,12,Fthat my residents and people right
OL,13,Facross the West Midlands rightly
OL,14,Fexpect and deserve?"
OL,16,FCommons Leader Lucy Powell MP said:
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@TO]
