OL,5,CAuthority
OL,7,F"I'm very sorry to hear about the poor
OL,8,Ffindings of the fire service in the
OL,9,FWest Midlands; it is a much-needed
OL,10,Fservice that local people should be
OL,11,Fable to rely on in those times of need.
OL,13,F"I don't have details of it with me
OL,14,Fnow, but I will ensure that the
OL,15,Frelevant minister gets back to her as
OL,16,Fsoon as possible about what can be
OL,17,Fdone."
