OL,7,FHer comments echoed that of Garry
OL,8,FPerry, the Leader of Walsall Council,
OL,9,Fwho made a similar request in a letter
OL,10,Fto the Home Secretary earlier this
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FIn a letter sent to staff yesterday,
OL,14,Fthe fire authority's vice chair,
OL,15,FCatherine Miks, acknowledged that the
OL,16,Fservice had been experiencing a
OL,17,F"challenging time."
