OL,7,FShe said "May I first say thank you to
OL,8,Fall of you for doing the critical work
OL,9,Fto keep our communities safe over what
OL,10,FI recognise has been a challenging
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"While I am disappointed in the series
OL,14,Fof events and consequent decisions of
OL,15,Fboth Oliver Lee and Councillor
OL,16,FBrackenridge to resign, I recognise
OL,17,Fthat these were their decisions to
OL,18,Ftake, and ours to navigate. I thank
OL,19,Fthem both for their work for WMFS."
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOU{D@cO]
