OL,7,F"We are in regular communication with
OL,8,Fthe Home Office and have invited any
OL,9,Fadditional scrutiny or support that
OL,10,Fthey may feel is necessary.
OL,12,F"We remain in close contact with them
OL,13,Fand are committed to ongoing
OL,14,Ftransparency.
OL,16,F"We are also in regular communication
OL,17,Fwith HMICFRS, and the Fire Authority
OL,18,Fhas written to them to formally
OL,19,Frequest a specific and focused review
OL,20,Fof the governance of the service.
